These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: martial-arts, spy, animation
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, ship, bike
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, june, august
House: craftsman, gothic-revival, farmhouse
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, marigold, tulip
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, orange, coral
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, hamster, goldfish
 1. the owner of the chinchilla is the person who likes orange##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is the farmhouse house##1
 3. the person watching animation movies is between the person who likes coral and the person watching spy movies##2
 4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 5. the gothic-revival house is the person driving the bike##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who likes blood-red##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person driving the van##1
 8. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
 9. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
10. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Movie-Genre      | spy    | animation   | martial-arts           |
| Transport          | ship       | bike    | van         |
| Birthday         | june    | august  | march        |
| House           | craftsman | gothic-revival   | farmhouse      |
| Flower   | marigold        | tulip    | poppy       |
| Color   | orange     | blood-red  | coral       |
| Pet         | chinchilla     | hamster | goldfish |

