.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway, helicopter
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, swisher, blend
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daffodil, sunflower, daisy
The people have 3 different jobs:  pilot, engineer, police-officer
The people have 3 different hobbies: hiking, board-games, cooking
3 different games are played: monopoly, billiard, chess
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, green, red
 1. the person playing chess is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the person playing chess is the person who growsdaisy##1
 3. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
 4. the person who likes white is between the person driving the subway and the person driving the quad-bike##2
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the subway is the pilot##1
 7. the engineer is on the left of the person who likes red##1
 8. the dannemann-smoker is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 9. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the police-officer##1
10. the person playing chess is on the left of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Transport      | quad-bike   | helicopter    | subway         |
| Cigar          | dannemann    | swisher | blend          |
| Flower   | daffodil  | daisy  | sunflower     |
| Job   | police-officer       | engineer      | pilot         |
| Hobby   | cooking      | board-games   | hiking    |
| Game           | monopoly        | chess      | billiard         |
| Color         | green | white  | red |

