.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, bike, subway
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, water, hot-chocolate
City: hamburg, rome, new-york
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, december, november
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, lilac, brown
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, journalist, musician
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, vegafina, montecristo
 1. the person driving the bike is the journalist##1
 2. the person who likes brown is the person drinking water##1
 3. the person traveling to hamburg is the person driving the subway##1
 4. the person traveling to rome is the journalist##1
 5. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 6. the person traveling to rome is on the left of the montecristo-smoker##1
 7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person who likes lilac and the person who's birthday is in november##2
 8. the person who likes lilac is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the journalist is on the right of the oliveros-smoker##1
10. the musician is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
11. the person who likes lilac is the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
| Transport          | subway      | bike      | tram      |
| Beverage         | cola   | hot-chocolate | water |
| City   | hamburg | rome    | new-york          |
| Birthday   | december       | april      | november          |
| Color   | lilac    | turquise  | brown      |
| Job           | nurse   | journalist  | musician        |
| Cigar         | oliveros  | vegafina   | montecristo     |

