The people use 3 different means of transport: helicopter, car, taxi
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bolivar, alhambra, swisher
3 different games are played: hannover, domino, scrabble
There 3 different types of food: zucchini, onion, banana
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, volleyball, swimming
 1. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
 2. the person who growsdaffodil is the person eating banana##1
 3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the swisher-smoker##1
 4. the person playing domino is on the right of the person playing hannover##1
 5. the person playing hannover is between the alhambra-smoker and the person who growsdaffodil##2
 6. the person who growsrose is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
 7. the person playing hannover is the person traveling to colone##1
 8. the person driving the helicopter is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 9. the person who growsrose is between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the taxi##2
10. the person eating banana is on the left of the person eating onion##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| Flower      | daffodil | rose           | daisy      |
| City         | hannover       | colone         | miami       |
| Transport           | helicopter    | car | taxi |
