 3. the person who growsorchid is the person traveling to colone##1
 4. the person who growsaconite is on the far right##1
 5. the person traveling to colone is between the person traveling to boston and the person who likes azure##2
 6. the person traveling to colone is between the person traveling to paris and the person playing go##2
 7. the person who's birthday is in december is between the chinese and the person who growsdaisy##2
 8. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
 9. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1
10. the person watching thriller movies is the chinese##1

.:: Answer ::.
