.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-17::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: black, grey, ebony
House: cottage, victorian, colonial
City: new-york, colone, san-francisco
The people have 3 different jobs:  freelancer, dressmaker, scientist
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: lily, daisy, marigold
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, bongani, baccarat
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, february, may
 1. the baccarat-smoker is in the middle##1
 2. the person who likes grey is in the middle##1
 3. the scientist is on the right of the cottage house##1
 4. the colonial house is the person traveling to colone##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the scientist##1
 6. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person traveling to colone##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in may is between the person who likes black and the freelancer##2
 8. the person traveling to new-york is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
 9. the person traveling to colone is the person who's birthday is in august##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is the freelancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Color      | black | grey      | ebony      |
| House         | cottage     | victorian     | colonial  |
| City   | san-francisco | new-york  | colone |
| Job   | dressmaker  | scientist     | freelancer |
| Flower           | lily        | marigold | daisy     |
| Cigar         | blend    | baccarat | bongani   |
| Birthday     | february        | may        | august   |

