.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-18::.
3 different pets are kept: snake, hedgehog, guinea-pig
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, dunhill, alhambra
There are 3 different nationalities: australian, japanese, indonesian
House: art-deco, gothic-revival, colonial
There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, chestnut, orange
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: trance, hip-hop, blues
3 different games are played: billiard, go, mah-jongg
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the colonial house##1
2. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the art-deco house##1
4. the fan trance is between the person who likes apricot and the gothic-revival house##2
5. the alhambra-smoker is between the colonial house and the indonesian##2
6. the japanese is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
7. the fan hip-hop is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
8. the person playing billiard is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
9. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the art-deco house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3      |
| Pet      | snake      | hedgehog      | guinea-pig       |
| Cigar          | dunhill      | alhambra    | aristoff   |
| Nationality         | indonesian    | australian     | japanese     |
| House           | gothic-revival    | art-deco | colonial   |
| Color   | chestnut    | orange    | apricot       |
| Music-Genre         | blues | trance      | hip-hop    |
| Game     | go       | billiard | mah-jongg |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-19::.
3 different pets are kept: goat, ferret, turtle
City: liverpool, paris, london
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, april, september
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: azalea, amaryllis, rose
House: tower, craftsman, townhouse
There are 3 different favourite colors: aquamarine, turquise, emerald
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, indonesian, french
1. the indonesian is the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
3. the person who likes emerald is on the right of the person who likes turquise##1
4. the person who growsrose is on the right of the french##1
5. the person traveling to paris is between the owner of the turtle and the person who's birthday is in june##2
6. the person traveling to london is on the right of the townhouse house##1
7. the owner of the goat is on the right of the craftsman house##1
8. the dutch is the person who growsrose##1
9. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |
| Pet      | turtle       | goat     | ferret         |
| City          | liverpool     | paris      | london     |
| Birthday         | april | september    | june      |
| Flower   | azalea   | amaryllis | rose    |
| House   | craftsman        | townhouse     | tower   |
| Color         | aquamarine     | turquise | emerald |
| Nationality     | indonesian     | french       | dutch    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-20::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, documentary, family
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, january, february
House: ranch-style, townhouse, futuristic
City: colone, berlin, san-francisco
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: bongani, dunhill, alhambra
3 different games are played: domino, billiard, snooker
There are 3 different favourite colors: blue, amber, white
1. the person watching animation movies is the person who's birthday is in february##1
2. the person who likes white is the person playing domino##1
3. the ranch-style house is between the person watching family movies and the alhambra-smoker##2
4. the person traveling to colone is on the left of the person who likes white##1
5. the bongani-smoker is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
6. the person who likes amber is on the left of the person who likes white##1
7. the townhouse house is the person who's birthday is in september##1
8. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the bongani-smoker##1
9. the person traveling to berlin is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who likes blue##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Movie-Genre      | documentary    | animation       | family      |
| Birthday          | september   | february   | january  |
| House           | townhouse  | ranch-style | futuristic    |
| City   | colone   | berlin     | san-francisco  |
| Cigar           | alhambra     | bongani        | dunhill |
| Game         | billiard | domino   | snooker  |
| Color     | amber    | white     | blue      |

 